{0:4:26 - 0:4:35} {CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (V.O.) (CONT'D)
{0:4:26 - 0:4:35} {DIALOGUE}: A Zippelback?
{0:4:33 - 0:4:35} {DIALOGUE}: Exotic, exciting.
{0:4:33 - 0:4:35} {DIALOGUE}: Two heads, twice the status.
{0:4:33 - 0:4:37} {DIALOGUE}: A second head pokes through the door and lights it.
{0:4:33 - 0:4:37} {DIALOGUE}: KABLAM!
{0:4:33 - 0:4:37} {DIALOGUE}: The two heads fly through the explosion, their necks zipping together to reveal a single body.
{0:4:33 - 0:4:37} {DIALOGUE}: It flies past Stoick as he climbs to the top of a CATAPULT
{0:4:33 - 0:4:37} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: TOWER.
{0:4:33 - 0:4:37} {CHARACTER_NAME}: CATAPULT OPERATOR
{0:4:35 - 0:4:37} {DIALOGUE}: They found the sheep!
{0:4:35 - 0:4:41} {CHARACTER_NAME}: STOICK
{0:4:35 - 0:4:41} {META_DATA}: (FRUSTRATED)
{0:4:35 - 0:4:41} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Concentrate fire over the lower bank!
