{0:28:59 - 0:29:7} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: "Dragon" DeBlois/Sanders Final Draft (Rev.19) 02-13-2010 38.
{0:28:59 - 0:29:7} {CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (CONT'D)
