{0:42:18 - 0:42:51} {SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. DOCKS - DAWN
{0:42:18 - 0:42:51} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A lone, battered ship is pulled into a slip, overloaded with equally battered-looking men.
{0:42:18 - 0:42:51} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They disembark to a crowd of onlookers, looking like a team of hometown heroes who just had their butts kicked.
{0:42:18 - 0:42:51} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Gobber hobbles through the MUMBLING crowd to find Stoick -- last to disembark and glowering with battered pride.
{0:42:18 - 0:42:51} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: "Dragon" DeBlois/Sanders Final Draft (Rev.19) 02-13-2010 51.
