{0:43:41 - 0:44:5} {DIALOGUE}: They roll off into an arcing bank, gloriously lit by the late afternoon sun.
{0:43:41 - 0:44:5} {DIALOGUE}: Hiccup tucks tight against his neck, thrilled that his new harness and vest are holding.
{0:43:41 - 0:44:5} {DIALOGUE}: The foot controls make the tail appendage quick and responsive.
{0:43:41 - 0:44:5} {DIALOGUE}: He watches Toothless' every fluctuation, trying to match it with the prosthetic.
