{0:45:5 - 0:46:5} {DIALOGUE}: Together, they manage a tight, hair-rasing series of split- second turns, making it to the open water, unscathed.
{0:45:5 - 0:46:5} {DIALOGUE}: Hiccup takes a breath and glances back at the death-defying obstacle course, now safely behind them.
