{0:53:29 - 0:53:37} {DIALOGUE}: Astrid SCREAMS.
{0:53:29 - 0:53:37} {DIALOGUE}: The acceleration is tremendous.
{0:53:29 - 0:53:37} {DIALOGUE}: Every downbeat bucks the saddle, heaving them into the sky, doubling their speed like a rocket.
{0:53:29 - 0:53:37} {DIALOGUE}: Astrid is thrown backward.
{0:53:29 - 0:53:37} {DIALOGUE}: She SCREAMS and hugs Hiccup for dear life, squeezing the breath out of him.
{0:53:29 - 0:53:37} {CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (CONT'D)
