{1:1:40 - 1:2:13} {DIALOGUE}: It tears out of its cave like an irate bull -- as the crowd roars and jeers.
{1:1:40 - 1:2:13} {DIALOGUE}: It climbs the walls and chain enclosure like a bat, hissing at the provoking crowd and blasting fire.
{1:1:40 - 1:2:13} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: "Dragon" DeBlois/Sanders Final Draft (Rev.19) 02-13-2010 72.
{1:1:40 - 1:2:13} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It spots Hiccup and descends, leering and licking the flaming drool from its lips.
{1:1:40 - 1:2:13} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The crowd grows silent, bracing for the big fight.
{1:1:40 - 1:2:13} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: With the Monstrous Nightmare's eyes locked upon him, Hiccup deliberately drops his shield and dagger stepping away from them.
{1:1:40 - 1:2:13} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The dragon pauses, confused.
