{1:13:53 - 1:14:8} {DIALOGUE}: A deep, rumbling ROAR echoes from the cavern.
{1:13:53 - 1:14:8} {DIALOGUE}: The ground underfoot TREMBLES.
{1:13:53 - 1:14:8} {DIALOGUE}: The ships rock.
{1:13:53 - 1:14:8} {DIALOGUE}: Their sails fill with a blast of air.
{1:13:53 - 1:14:8} {DIALOGUE}: The cheering stops.
{1:13:53 - 1:14:8} {DIALOGUE}: Stoick's expression sinks.
{1:13:53 - 1:14:8} {CHARACTER_NAME}: STOICK
{1:14:3 - 1:14:8} {DIALOGUE}: This isn't over.
