{1:14:21 - 1:14:34} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: "Dragon" DeBlois/Sanders Final Draft (Rev.19) 02-13-2010 87.
{1:14:21 - 1:14:34} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The ground CRACKS.
{1:14:21 - 1:14:34} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Stone tears away, cascading like an avalanche.
{1:14:21 - 1:14:34} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: And through the settling debris, the silhouette of a gargantuan dragon emerges -- THE RED DEATH.
{1:14:21 - 1:14:34} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Stirred and furious.
