{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: STOICK explodes to the surface, pulling Hiccup to the shoreline through flaming debris.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: He lays him down, under the shelter of an overhanging rock.
