{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {META_DATA}: (OVERWHELMED)
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Dad... Stoick dives back into the water between flaming flotsam.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {CHARACTER_NAME}: UNDERWATER
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: ON TOOTHLESS, drowning.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: Stoick appears in front of him.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: Toothless freezes.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: Stoick tears the chains off of the yoke and lets it float free.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: Momentary stillness.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: They eye each other, through the churned up bubbles.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: Toothless lunges out of the bars -- grabbing Stoick.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: BOOM!
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: In an explosion of sea water, Toothless lands on the shore, setting Stoick down and releasing him.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: Hiccup is awed.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: The ground rumbles underfoot.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: The monster screeches.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: Its massive claws stomp around in the smoke.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: Stoick gives way as Toothless mounts the rock and raises his wings.
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: He turns to Hiccup and SNORTS - Let's go.'
{1:17:53 - 1:18:54} {CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (CONT'D)
{1:18:52 - 1:18:54} {DIALOGUE}: You got it, bud.
{1:18:52 - 1:18:58} {DIALOGUE}: Hiccup climbs onto Toothless and buckles himself in.
{1:18:52 - 1:18:58} {DIALOGUE}: Stoick grabs his arm.
{1:18:52 - 1:18:58} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: "Dragon" DeBlois/Sanders Final Draft (Rev.19) 02-13-2010 94.
{1:18:52 - 1:18:58} {CHARACTER_NAME}: STOICK
{1:18:57 - 1:18:58} {DIALOGUE}: Hiccup.
