{1:22:48 - 1:23:36} {DIALOGUE}: It throws open its wings, attempting to put on the brakes, but the punctured, damaged wings can't stop its momentum.
{1:22:48 - 1:23:36} {DIALOGUE}: As the Red Death chokes on the expanding fireball, he sees Toothless suddenly pull out of the dive, streaking up, past its head.
{1:22:48 - 1:23:36} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: "Dragon" DeBlois/Sanders Final Draft (Rev.19) 02-13-2010 99.
{1:22:48 - 1:23:36} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Red Death HITS the ground, head-first.
