{1:27:38 - 1:27:44} {META_DATA}: (bittersweet, coming to
{1:27:38 - 1:27:44} {CHARACTER_NAME}: TERMS)
{1:27:42 - 1:27:44} {DIALOGUE}: I might make a few tweaks.
{1:27:42 - 1:27:47} {DIALOGUE}: Astrid appears and jabs Hiccup in the arm.
{1:27:42 - 1:27:47} {DIALOGUE}: Hiccup recoils with a grumble.
{1:27:42 - 1:27:47} {CHARACTER_NAME}: ASTRID
{1:27:46 - 1:27:47} {DIALOGUE}: That's for scaring me.
{1:27:46 - 1:27:54} {CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP
