{1:27:58 - 1:28:2} {DIALOGUE}: Suddenly, Toothless pounces on the crowd, crushing several unsuspecting Vikings under his weight.
{1:27:58 - 1:28:2} {CHARACTER_NAME}: VIKING
{1:28:0 - 1:28:2} {DIALOGUE}: Night Fury, get down!
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {DIALOGUE}: Toothless eyes the new tail excitedly, tongue wagging.
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {DIALOGUE}: Amidst the groans and grumbles, Hiccup and Astrid exchange a sheepish grin.
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {META_DATA}: CLOSE ON
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {CHARACTER_NAME}: CLOSE ON
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {DIALOGUE}: Hiccup's prosthetic foot, snapping into the modified stirrup.
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: "Dragon" DeBlois/Sanders Final Draft (Rev.19) 02-13-2010 105.
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The two pieces click together, forming a single shape.
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Astride Toothless, he's whole again.
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He rotates the pedal.
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The new tail opens.
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Bright red with a skull and Viking horns emblazoned on it.
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hiccup approves.
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {META_DATA}: CUT BACK TO REVEAL...
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Hiccup and Toothless, saddled up and ready to fly.
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Astrid backs her Nadder into position.
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {META_DATA}: (TO TOOTHLESS)
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: You ready?
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Toothless SNORTS an excited 'yes!'
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: From his mount, Hiccup looks out over the changed world.
{1:28:0 - 1:28:19} {CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (V.O.) (CONT'D)
{1:28:16 - 1:28:19} {DIALOGUE}: This... is Berk.
{1:28:16 - 1:28:28} {META_DATA}: (BEAT)
{1:28:16 - 1:28:28} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: It snows nine months of the year... and hails the other three.
{1:28:16 - 1:28:28} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They LEAP into the bright blue sky, together as one.
{1:28:16 - 1:28:28} {SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Astrid follows, giving chase.
{1:28:16 - 1:28:28} {CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (CONT'D)
{1:28:24 - 1:28:28} {DIALOGUE}: Any food that grows here is tough and tasteless.
{1:28:30 - 1:28:33} {DIALOGUE}: The people that grow here are even more so.
{1:28:30 - 1:28:39} {DIALOGUE}: Hiccup and Astrid race their dragons through the village -- under eaves, over rooftops, down cliff-sides, and between ship masts.
{1:28:30 - 1:28:39} {DIALOGUE}: It's a high energy, romantic dance of sorts.
{1:28:30 - 1:28:39} {CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (V.O.) (CONT'D)
{1:28:37 - 1:28:39} {DIALOGUE}: The only upsides are the pets.
{1:28:42 - 1:28:45} {DIALOGUE}: While other places have...ponies or parrots, we have... Their fellow recruits join them as they take to the open sky, rocketing far above the village.
{1:28:42 - 1:28:51} {DIALOGUE}: The Northern sky swirls with blazing, multicolored dragons.
{1:28:42 - 1:28:51} {DIALOGUE}: Hiccup and Toothless break from the pack, spinning into the blinding sun.
{1:28:42 - 1:28:51} {CHARACTER_NAME}: HICCUP (V.O.) (CONT'D)
{1:28:42 - 1:28:51} {META_DATA}: (PROUDLY)
{1:28:49 - 1:28:51} {DIALOGUE}: ... dragons.
{1:28:49 - 1:28:52} {META_DATA}: FADE TO WHITE
